## Existing test infrastructure to reuse

The test file already provides:
- `mockRuntime` object with all `AgentRuntime` methods mocked via `vi.fn()`
- `S1` constant: `'00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001'` — valid UUID for session ID
- `request(app)` via `supertest` — already imported
