## Validating the fix

This test should FAIL before Task 1.4 is applied (the request would hang until a timeout, or return an unexpected status). After Task 1.4 wraps the handler in try/catch with `next(err)`, Express error middleware sends a 500 response immediately.

## Acceptance Criteria

- The test passes after Task 1.4 is applied
- The test FAILS (or hangs) if the try/catch from Task 1.4 is removed
- Response status is `500` (not `503` or a timeout)
- Response body contains an `error` field
- All other existing `sessions.test.ts` tests continue to pass
- Running `pnpm vitest run apps/server/src/routes/__tests__/sessions.test.ts` passes all tests
